&lt;h2 id="introduction">Introduction
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>Just by the title, I roughly grasped the song&amp;rsquo;s meaning, and it also triggered my past thoughts on life. Before, I could never find an answer to &amp;ldquo;why live?&amp;rdquo;. But, flipping it, &amp;ldquo;why not end it?&amp;rdquo;. I explored ways to commit suicide and their consequences. I realized I feared suicide. So, because of that fear, I chose to live. This perfectly aligns with the song.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>